  <title>Retrieve a color ramp from the SymbologyControl</title>
  <purpose><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:my="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/infopath/2003/myXSD/2006-02-10T23:25:53">This sample demonstrates how to retrieve a color ramp from the SymbologyControl and use it within a ClassBreaksRenderer. The sample uses the SymbologyControl in conjunction with the PageLayoutControl, ToolbarControl, and the controls commands.</div></purpose>
